dcterms:description: The AfriWOZ dataset is a collection of dialogue data for 6 African languages, consisting of 1,500 turns each, translated from the English MultiWOZ dataset. It is designed for training and evaluating open-domain dialogue models.
dcterms:title: AfriWOZ
dcterms:language: Swahili, Wolof, Hausa, Nigerian Pidgin English, Kinyarwanda, Yorùbá

dcterms:creator: Paweł Budzianowski
Tsung-Hsien Wen
Bo-Hsiang Tseng
Iñigo Casanueva
Stefan Ultes
Osman Ramadan
Milica Gašić
dcterms:description: MultiWOZ is a large-scale multi-domain Wizard-of-Oz dataset for task-oriented dialogue modelling, consisting of human-human written conversations that span multiple domains and topics.
dcterms:title: MultiWOZ
